Missing Clickjacking Protection Header

Location
  https://lp-cashchego.vercel.app/

Description

The server didn't return a X-Frame-Options header as part of its HTTP response, which enables clickjacking attacks against it since its content is allowed to be embedded into other sites.

Content Security Policy (CSP) Not Enabled

Location
  https://lp-cashchego.vercel.app/

Description

The server didn't return a Content-Security-Policy (CSP) header as part of its HTTP response. By not implementing a CSP, you miss an extra layer of security against attacks such as cross-site scripting (XSS), clickjacking and other issues.

Solution
